description: The right-learning business community on Twitter, including Elon Musk and hedge fund billionaire Bill Ackman, used their megaphones to endorse Trump and fuel storylines about Saturday’s attack.
title: Musk, other pro-Trump billionaires have helped shape shooting narrative

description: Researchers who track online conspiracies say liberals, too, are now vulnerable to -- and generating -- QAnon-like bursts of misinformation.
title: ‘BlueAnon’ conspiracy theories flood social media after Trump rally shooting
